      "content": "I see. So you're saying there's a specific cultural \"nuance\" there. If we were looking at a white student with the exact same behaviors—loud, interrupting, hyper—would the professional approach be different? Would we be more likely to jump to a clinical diagnosis like ADHD for a white student instead of attributing it to culture?",
